cff-version: 1.2.0
title: PromeTorch
message: If you use this software in your research, please cite it as below.
type: software
authors:
  - name: PromeTorch contributors
repository-code: 'https://github.com/barometech/PromeTorch'
abstract: >-
  PromeTorch is a from-scratch PyTorch-compatible deep learning framework
  written in C++17 with CUDA and CPU backends, including a fully featured
  GGUF inference runtime, multi-process tensor-parallel decoding for the
  Эльбрус 8C2 VLIW architecture, and a custom NMC4 (NM Card / NM Quad)
  fixed-point quantization backend.
keywords:
  - deep-learning
  - inference
  - llm
  - gguf
  - cuda
  - elbrus
  - nm-card
  - quantization
  - tensor-parallel
license: SEE LICENSE
